This is an implementation of the Number to LCD kata written in python using 
an object oriented + test driven development approach.

Thinking that represemting LCD digits as raw strings is probably not right, takinh a littlr btrak yo yhink tkis out

Python: 3.11.4
Packages: pytest, pylint

To run the application:
    python app.py

To run the test:
    pytest

To lint the project:
    find . -type f -name "*.py" | xargs pylint
